- Tools update
  you can use submodule or download to this folder directly!!!
  ```
  git submodule 
     387dd93f7fe8bba60e3bd7f461d1012ea6590842 rvos_tools (heads/master)

  git submodule update --init
  ```
  
- Install docker with linux
  ```
  sudo apt-get install docker.io
  ```
  you can choose other methods in your mac/windows OS.
  
- Build docker
  ```
  sudo docker build -t riscv_os_sdk:latest .
  sudo docker images
  ```
  if apt is slower while building, you can change the apt source list of 
  source docker image.

  
- Run docker
  ```
  sudo docker run --rm -it -v $PWD:/root/ riscv_os_sdk:latest /bin/bash
  ```
  refer to https://docs.docker.com/reference/

